metadata.description: Eyes closed and heart open, you step inside a portal to the unknown. Feeling a mix of fear and excitement, you wonder: Where will it take me? A prismatic gust of wind envelopes your body as curiosity rushes through your spirit. Right now. This is it. The infinity awaits you. You open your eyes: you have entered your very own world within the Magic Mind universe.
metadata.name: Magic Mind World #1
